Trade Vehicle and Water Jetting Specialists

With over 50 years of industry experience, Enviroline has built a reputation as a trusted leader in trade vehicle fitouts, high-performance water jetters, and pipe maintenance equipment across Australia. Proudly Australian-made and built in our Sydney-based warehouse, our solutions are designed to meet the demands of tradies—offering durability, innovation, and performance you can count on.

Trade Vehicle Fitouts

Complete Turnkey Solutions. Designed for Productivity. Built to Last.

Ute Fitouts

Explore ute fit-outs

Our trade ute fitouts are proudly Australian made, crafted with high-quality materials and engineered to meet the demands of hardworking professionals.

We provide a complete, end-to-end solution, managing everything from vehicle sourcing and full fitouts to vinyl wrap branding, registration, and financing. Best of all, we can deliver directly to your door anywhere in Australia.

Getting your trade ute on the road has never been easier or more stress-free.

Van Fitouts

Explore van fit-outs

Our modular trade van fitouts are expertly designed and proudly Australian made, using high-quality materials to meet the demands of busy tradies and service professionals.

From vehicle sourcing, custom racking and storage systems to van accessories and branded vinyl wraps, we handle it all. With in-house financing and delivery available anywhere in Australia, getting your fully equipped trade van on the road has never been easier.

Who we work with

Industries we work with

We work closely with the plumbing, electrical, and HVAC industries to deliver premium, Australian-made vehicle fitouts—purpose-built to suit the demands of every trade and construction job.

Plumbing

With over 50 years in the plumbing industry, Enviroline specialises in Australian-made water jetters and pipe maintenance accessories—making us the go-to, one-stop shop for all your plumbing equipment needs.

Electrical

Stay on top of every job with a vehicle fitout suited to the needs of electricians. Our systems are designed for ease of access, smart storage, and everyday durability. Whether you’re upgrading a single van or fitting out an entire fleet, we offer practical solutions that help keep your equipment secure and your business running smoothly.

HVAC

For heating, ventilation, and air conditioning professionals, having a well-organised and dependable vehicle setup is key. Enviroline’s HVAC fitouts are built to handle the demands of mobile service work—supporting fast access, safe storage, and efficient jobsite performance.

Construction

Built for the demands of the construction industry, our trade ute fitouts are tough and reliable. From tool storage to site-ready setups, we deliver Australian-made solutions that help construction professionals stay organised, efficient, and ready to work.
